<![CDATA[<p><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></p>
<p><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">My name is {!Account.OwnerFullName} and I am the Account Manager at WEX Fleet One assigned to help make sure you get the most out of your WEX Fleet One Account.</font></p>
<p><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2">Per my voice mail, I not only wanted to introduce myself, but also make certain you were aware of everything WEX Fleet One can </font><font size="2">can offer you to manage your company's vehicles.</font></font></p><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">
